reviewText:
Really adictive,worth a try. I really like the atmosphere in it too. Crafting sistem is quite intresting, you can find some recipes or get it from quests.

Can't wait for Dead Island 2 and some familiar games to it


secretly I really enjoy games that have beautiful nature/beach themes ;3;

Dead Island Riptide follows the story of the original dead island. ( My Dead Island Review )

The gameplay of DI:R doesn't differ that much from the original. It's still the same zombie grinder simulator, but there is some new features.

Cool new stuff
New colorful locations;
New zombies;
New vehicles (boats);
More weapons, mods & blueprints;
More gore;
The level cap has been raised to 70;
And some new dynamic weather system and hub defense missions, where you can upgrade the characters in your current base and they'll get better stores and better weapons.
And there is also a new playable character.
» John, which focus on hand-to-hand combat.

You can import your character from the original dead island and they'll keep the level & skills.


This game is better than the original in every way. Get both if you can, if not, get this one.
